originalText.text: I spent the summer in the city and needed a cleaning, so I made an appointment with Dr. Rogosin. From the receptionist’s desk to the cleaning itself, I felt comfortable and cared for. Dr. Rogosin was terrific—very attentive and kind. Highly recommend!

originalText.text:
Exceptional
Can't stop smiling! Thankful for the great experience and quality work Dr. Rogosin has done on my teeth throughout the years. She takes her time to explain every procedure and made sure that she also understands my concerns. She is a true professional and has such a lovely personality. I would recommend Dr. Rogosin to everyone. She is the best dentist I have ever had.

originalText.text: Dr Rogosin is a kind and proficient dentist.  Before going to her I had some dental anxiety issues.  They disappeared once I started using her.  She explains all your options and together you decide the best course of events.  She is gentle in your mouth  and efficient with her time.  I would highly recommend her.  Also the office staff is so kind and true professionals as well.  A plus office!!!

originalText.text: Dr. Rogosin has been my dentist for 8 years, and I recommend her with high regard. She is prompt, friendly, and engaging. Professionally, she takes time with you as a patient and allows for questions and answers. She is highly skilled and uses the most recent practices available. Her office is clean and inviting, and her staff is professional and courteous. The office is easily accessible from the BC and 1 trains.
